parameters:
\SE\SE[21]Wow... What a beautiful view. \SE[21]I wish I
could have shown it to Luna too...

\SE[2]Geez, all you guys ever think about is that.
\!\SE[79]...It's fine that you get along well, but...

\SE[88]There's something I've been hesitating about for a
long time... \SE[51]I was a little scared to ask, though...

\SE[85]I wonder if it's okay for me to continue following
everyone like this? \SE[93]Is it okay for me to be with
them... Do I have the qualifications?
\SE[2] Qualifications? I wonder what that means?

\SE[85]I don't have a reason to keep fighting. I just want
to be with Luna... \SE[86]Is it okay for me to be with her
so casually... Can I continue being with her?

\SE[75]You don't need to worry about that. \SE[4]I think as
long as you're in your favorite place, it's fine.

\SE[85]It seems like I can't bring myself to hate people...
\SE[44]Certainly, I've seen bad people too...

\SE[85]Surely, those people also have their own...
\.unavoidable circumstances, right? \!\SE[86]Just like me...
\.Maybe they never had the option to begin with.

\SE[85]If I think like that... I can't have a strong purpose
like revenge... \SE[93]Is it okay for me to be with everyone
with these half- hearted feelings...

\SE[74]I think it's strange for me to speak so confidently
when I'm the one who got involved in all this trouble...
\SE[3]But still, if there's one thing I can say...

\SE[2]What you're thinking is, Because you want to be with
someone, right? ...Rather, isn't that the only motivation
you have? \SE[75]Everyone is fighting because they want to
protect their family.

\SE[73]I... I want to live without any regrets. \SE[50]I
don't know what my end will be like, but...

\SE[2]I absolutely don't want to experience such miserable
regret like If only I had made that choice at that time....
\SE[19]Even if it leads to any kind of outcome, I want to be
strong and exist after making my own choices.

\SE[52]I have no intention of imposing my way of life on
you, of course... \!\SE[3]I like you, and I don't want you
to carry such miserable regrets.

\SE[50]...I don't even know what I want to say anymore.
\SE[75]It's not like me to engage in self-indulgent
monologues like this...

\SE[2]There's a well ahead. I'll go fetch some water.
\SE[3]...You should get some fresh air for a bit.

\SE[85]I... want to become stronger. \SE[44]Not just me
being protected by Luna... but me standing alongside Luna...
